    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Superfamily Portunoidea Rafinesque, 1815, dorsal habitus: A, Charybdis hellerii (A. Milne-Edwards, 1867), male, cw 69.3 mm (BLSZ 019); B, Cronius ruber (Lamarck, 1818), male, cw 13.1 mm (BLSZ 062); C, Laleonectes vocans (A. Milne-Edwards, 1878), male, cw 20.0 mm (MZUSP 40913); D, Portunus sayi (Gibbes, 1850), female, cw 38.0 mm (BLSZ 205). Scale bars: A, C, D = 20 mm; B = 5 mm." ;
